Implement transaction encoding (Phase 1)

Add binary serialisation for Bitcoin transactions using
Data.ByteString.Builder:

- Internal helpers: put_compact (compactSize/varint encoding),
  put_word32_le, put_word64_le, to_strict
- Component encoders: put_outpoint, put_txin, put_txout, put_witness
- Main functions: to_bytes (segwit-aware), to_bytes_legacy

to_bytes emits segwit format (marker 0x00, flag 0x01, witnesses after
outputs) when witnesses are present, otherwise delegates to legacy.
to_bytes_legacy always emits legacy format (no marker/flag/witnesses),
used for txid computation.

